text: Katherine Evelyn Anita Cassidy (also Katie Cassidy; born November 25, 1986) is an American actress. She played Kris Fowles in A Nightmare on Elm Street (the 2010 movie). She also played Ruby in the series Supernatural. Cassidy was born in Los Angeles. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:1986 births Category:Living people
